structure.unit: JUVENILE PROCEEDINGS -- COMMITMENT AND CARE OF CHILDREN

law.history: Repealed 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 157, sec. 54, effective February 27, 1956. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 50, effective January 1, 1953.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Children paroled by youth authority exempt from responsibility or authority of division of probation and parole.
